  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc2\u0bb0 \u0baa\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Radhakrishnan demands regular distribution of cooking gas to remote areas in Nuwara Eliya",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Leader of the Upcountry People's Front Vee. Radhakrishnan MP Demanded.",
        "Radhakrishnan, who was traveling to Kotagala today, had a discussion with the 'Lap Case' agent there.",
        "Asked about the crisis situation in the proper distribution of cooking gas, he also pointed out the complaints lodged by the people.",
        "Although gas was distributed to urban areas in the midst of the crisis but did not reach the plantation areas in remote areas, he therefore asked them to take action for this.",
        "Pushpa Viswanathan, Finance Secretary of the Upcountry Workers Front and members and officials were present."
      ],
